{"type":"message","id":"3930b5e7","parentId":"9c9ddf40","timestamp":"2026-03-26T02:09:23.652Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is the backticks `**` in the JSON string. The `**` characters in the JSON content are causing the JSON parsing to fail because they interfere with the string delimiters. \n\nWait, the content is a JSON string where the entire JSON is the `content` parameter. The `**` shouldn't cause issues with JSON parsing per se, unless the outer JSON parser is having issues with the markdown bold syntax.\n\nActually, looking at my test message that worked:\n```\n{\"text\":\"test\"}\n```\n\nAnd the failing ones use `**` inside the text. The issue might be that `**` characters are being interpreted in some way. \n\nLet me try escaping them or using a different approach. \n\nI realize the problem is that markdown bold syntax like `**` in a JSON string doesn't actually render as bold in Feishu text messages—it's treated as literal characters. So I need to strip out the markdown formatting entirely and send just the plain text, since Feishu's text messages don't support that formatting anyway.\n\nBut there's a bigger issue: I actually sent Wang Yuanhao a shortened version with missing text, which is what Yao Zong flagged. I can't use markdown bold syntax in the API call at all. The only viable path forward is sending plain text without any bold markers, but that means Yao Zong won't see bold in the confirmation versions he reviews—though he'll still see it in the final messages. Before sending anything else, I need to correct Wang Yuanhao's message by sending the exact full text without bold markers, and I'm trying to figure out why my last attempt with ** didn't work.","thinkingSignature":"ef86b70ea4fc2757c1aef15b1f109015c84aa65eb89fd7c4a0649f2f1e8a4fb7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vo05wvw9xa6x_1","name":"feishu_im_user_message","arguments":{"action":"send","receive_id_type":"open_id","receive_id":"ou_0a41155c9f7ed341a3c314470ad4768c","msg_type":"text","content":"{\"text\":\"**道简网络总经理助理**：王垣皓日报点评如下：\\n\\n做得好的：\\n- 晨会承诺100%兑现：农业大棚视频会议和水务局方案均按时完成，体现了较强的执行力，是对自己承诺负责的表现。\\n- 主动承担多项目并行：当天涉及农业大棚、水务局、铭云科技、胶州项目4个工作项，覆盖面广，体现了积极的工作态度。\\n\\n需改进：\\n- 拜访数量严重不达标：全天仅1次客户拜访（铭云科技），距离3次最低标准差距明显。拜访是销售推进项目、获取商机的核心动作，数量不足将直接影响业绩产出。\\n- 日报结果意识极度薄弱：4项工作没有一项写了明确结果。\"参加视频会议\"不知道结论是什么；\"出方案\"不知道是否提交；\"拜访铭云科技\"不知道谈了什么；\"对胶州项目\"不知道方案确认没有。管理者完全无法通过日报判断项目真实进展。\\n- 经验沉淀完全空洞：\"提高方案解决速读\"6个字，既无方法论、又无案例支撑、更无可操作性，是敷衍了事的典型。好的经验沉淀应该写清楚：今天哪项工作用了什么方法，速度提升了多少，对后续工作有什么指导意义。\\n- 明日计划缺乏落地性：\"见面客户对方案\"——见谁？方案核心是什么？要达成什么目标？这些都是空白，计划写了等于没写。\\n\\n建议：\\n- 立即提升拜访量：明天（03-26）计划中必须包含至少3次客户现场拜访，减少案头工作时间，把更多精力放在客户当面沟通上。\\n- 日报必须逐项写清楚结果：每一项工作后面必须跟上【结果：xxx / 下一步：xxx】，这是刚性要求，不能只写\"做了xxx\"。\\n- 重新撰写经验沉淀：请结合今天实际工作，认真思考今天出方案、拜访客户的过程中，有哪些具体方法可以复用，写清楚方法、效果、可复制性。\\n- 明日计划必须完善：每次拜访前想清楚拜访目的（确认报价/签约/获取需求/推进方案），计划中体现这个目的，而非笼统写\"见面客户\"。\\n\\n总分：39分\"}"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":40873,"output":889,"cacheRead":56355,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98117,"cost":{"input":0.0122619,"output":0.0010668,"cacheRead":0.00169065,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.015019349999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774490939830}}
