{"type":"message","id":"0bdeb95a","parentId":"fccf5f1b","timestamp":"2026-03-26T04:56:22.559Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"四名员工的日报点评已全部发送：\n- 王文强 ✅\n- 王垣皓 ✅\n- 郝彦艳 ✅\n- 刘晓 ✅\n\n接下来需要进行归档3步法。","thinkingSignature":"e69b77d2b1c0389773ac2368c5272d337caaf5260df728ba4cbe38ceff369ac8"},{"type":"text","text":"前四名员工日报点评已全部发送：\n- 王文强 ✅\n- 王垣皓 ✅\n- 郝彦艳 ✅\n- 刘晓 ✅\n\n接下来需要进行归档3步法（确认版文档、多维表格录入、汇总索引更新），是否继续执行？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":102300,"output":101,"cacheRead":56355,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":158756,"cost":{"input":0.03069,"output":0.00012119999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00169065,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03250185}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774500978306}}
